metadata.name: STARSTRUCK PUFFER
metadata.description:
The STARSTRUCK PUFFER is a limited edition physical/digital lightweight jacket made for both the digital and physical world.  

Sizing: Jackets run true to size  , please order your regular size upon claim.

Each holder is entitled to anonymously claim 1x jacket free of charge via a short claim window in the official TEJITOPIA discord: https://discord.com/invite/TXtPXkWjSv
